          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2421Step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Add 400ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[800ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> to a pot over a medium heat with the <strong>chopped inner core<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> of the lemongrass and 1/2 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</span></p>\n<p>Cook for 2 min until fragrant</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>baby button mushrooms</strong> finely</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
